N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4626.8 - Hearings open to public

State Regulations

All hearings on suspension and revocation of licenses or
identification numbers or imposition of fines, held by the commission, shall be
open to the public. Notes
